nikṛṣṭānāṃ tu bhedamayānāṃ tadasiddhyai śivādvayasādhanābhāvāya kāni nāvaraṇāni tīkṣṇatamayuktyastrāṇyapi samāveśarasavipruṣo 'py anabhijñatvādasañcetyamānāni mahāndhakārapātayitṝṇyeva |

